  "body": "- [ ] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nTruffle console works with errors with node v12.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nUse node v12. Run truffle console. Compile. Migrate. try to interact with a contract. let contract = await Token.deployed(). Get the error.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nNo errors\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nUncaught ReferenceError: global is not defined at evalmachine.<anonymous>:2:19\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: MasOS\r\n* Ethereum client: Ganache\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): v5.1.51 (core: 5.1.51)\r\n* node version (`node --version`): v12.22.4\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`): 6.14.14\r\n",
